{"groups":[{"groupKey":"120363422965145348@g.us","name":"120363422965145348@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":32,"lastActive":1783496779225,"messages":[{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Hello. Flight AA281 is delayed. New expected landing time is 5:55pm. Thank you","ts":1783441710216},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Then, how many passengers are arriving on UA 893 and AA 281 respectively?","ts":1783444846382},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"UA 893 is 4 people\nAA281 is 3 people\n7 people total\n\n1 person switched to tomorrow","ts":1783445244877},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"First group is able tp wait for second group at airport.","ts":1783445316861},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"The waiting time will probably be too long\n\nSo We'll arrange one car for UA 893 (4 people) and one for AA 281 (3 people)\n\nHow about this?","ts":1783445490194},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Great! Thank you! First car name for UA893 is for Jeffrey. \nI will be on the AA281","ts":1783445577642},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Ok noted.See you soon 😀","ts":1783445717886},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Thank you!!!","ts":1783445735649},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"AA281 new arrival time 7:01","ts":1783452184597},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Sorry 8:01","ts":1783453294868},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Don't worry. The driver will track your flight and check your arrival time","ts":1783458284579},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @190061194801246 \n\nMy name is Cyrus Noh, and I’ll be your check-in host today.\n\nI’m here to help make your arrival smooth and comfortable, and to guide you through anything you may need for your check-in. 🏠✨\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783477737405},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"when you go out to arrival hall, please find out your name board.","ts":1783477783793},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello 😊 I’ve invited today’s driver @66941494517817 to this group chat for easier coordination.","ts":1783478270954},{"sender":"Tom Hegdal","text":"First group is looking for the driver.","ts":1783492830405},{"sender":"Tom Hegdal","text":"They are in the arrival hall by E","ts":1783492974535},{"sender":"AirportVan","text":"We have already met.","ts":1783493016938},{"sender":"Tom Hegdal","text":"Ah . Thank you very much. Yes, that is them","ts":1783493030000},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Here we share the information of home and service :)","ts":1783495043294},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Home Address :","ts":1783495043888},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"서울 마포구 성미산로23길 16-5  2층","ts":1783495044449},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"2F, 16-5, Seongmisan-ro 23-gil, Mapo-gu, Seoul, Republic of Korea","ts":1783495045045},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Neighborhood information !","ts":1783495045620},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Front Door Pin 2 6 0 7 3 1 *","ts":1783495046198},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"[NAVER Map]\nCOZE YT \nhttps://naver.me/5JpRM6v7","ts":1783495046769},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"House Manual (BIRD 09)","ts":1783495047325},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"🏠 *BIRD 09 Guest Manual*\n\n📌 Essential Information\n\nAddress — \n\n서울 마포구 성미산로23길 16-5  \n16-5, Seongmisan-ro 23-gil, Mapo-gu, Seoul, Republic of Korea\n\nYour Suite Door Code — Check‑in date in the format YYMMDD + *\nExample: 10 May 2025 → 250510* (remains the same throughout your stay)\n\nWi‑Fi Networks\n\nSSID  KT_GiGA_C355 \nPIN    0dk93gg800 \n\n\n📱 Guest Smartphone Provided\n\nA free smartphone with a Korean number and unlimited data & calls is available on the living room table. It comes preloaded with essential apps and can be used as a Wi-Fi hotspot.\n💡 Tip: Check out Naver Map’s Bookmarks for local restaurants, stores, banks, hospitals, and hidden gems!\n\n🍽️ Food Delivery\n\nUse the smart phone for guest to open Coupang Eats, create your cart, and send us a screenshot of your final order via Messenger. We’ll pay and place the order — just leave payment (cash or crypto) when checking out.\n\n🚐 MPV Van Taxi\nLet us know if you need a van. We’ll help arrange peer-to-peer transport options.\n\n🍳 Kitchen Appliances\n\nA full kitchen includes: dishwasher, oven, water purifier.\n\n\n💧 Water Purifier (EVERPURE)\nBrand: EVERPURE (USA) — Starbucks official partner\n\nType: Direct-flow purified water system\n\nMaintenance: Professionally serviced monthly\n\nHow to use: Use the small faucet on the left side of the sink labeled “정수기 / Purified Water.”\n\nBenefit: Very safe, great-tasting water for drinking & cooking\n\nFeel free to cook like home!\n\n☕ Capsule Coffee & Tea\nExtra capsules & tea bags are in the drawer above the multi-cooker oven.\nilly Coffee Machine Guide:\n\nQuick Start: https://youtu.be/XEDAXZY50FM?si=uOfwquZXC6WCis_G\n\nSteam Milk: https://youtu.be/bTzG7iM4dMA?si=aiEWUseiOT0as-Jo\n\nVolume Settings: https://youtu.be/h2X5gLYpf_4?si=eaDtARcyGQTjddFz\n\n\n♻️ Food Waste Disposal\nUse the sink disposer: run water, press foot pedal.\n\n🗑️ Trash & Recycling\nBins for general/recycling waste are near the entrance.\n\n📺 2nd Floor TV\nConnected to Google TV, cable, and a PC. Netflix, Disney+, YouTube & more. HDMI cable behind TV for external devices.\n\n🧻 Towels & Tissues\nStored under the kitchen island.\n\n🎁 Amenities\n\n🛋️ Motion Bed & Bedding\n2nd-floor sofa = 2 beds via remote. Extra mattresses/blankets are in the living room cabinet next to the fire extinguisher.\n\n🪟 Windows & Blinds\nPrivacy film blocks view by day. At night, close blinds. Big blinds in living room = wall remote.\n\n***Blinds\nPrivacy film blocks view by day. At night, close blinds. Big blinds in living room = wall remote.\n\n\n\n❄️  A/C Notice\nIf you set the mode as 'AD' or 'Automatic' in remote controller, the A/C will be turned off when its temperature reach to 25 degree(celcius) So PLEASE SET THE MODE as COOLING \n\n🚭 Smoking\nAllowed on each floor’s balcony. Use ashtray provided.\n\n🛏️ Loft Room\nQueen bed, ventilation, cozy but low ceiling. Be careful on stairs!\n\n🚗 Where to park\n • We don’t have a private lot, but most guests leave their car along the curb right beside the building.\n (Technically it isn’t legal, yet enforcement is rare.)\n\n\n• Only a 3-minute walk away you’ll find the \n\nYeonnam-dong Public Parking Lot. 📍\nMap → https://naver.me/x0UvYEAj\n\nAddress │ 361-9 Yeonnam-dong, Mapo-gu, Seoul\n\n Rate │ ₩300 per 5 minutes (no all-day pass)\n\n Discount │ 50 % off for multi-child families & eco-friendly vehicles\n\n\n💬 Inquiries & Assistance\nGot questions? Message us via Messenger anytime. We’ll reply quickly and gladly help!\n\n💬📱☕️\nEnjoy your COZE stay and relax like a local!","ts":1783495047898},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"🏠 *FISH 09 Guest Manual*\n\n📌 Essential Information\n\n📍 Address\n \n\n서울 마포구 성미산로23길 16-5\n 16-5,\n Seongmisan-ro 23-gil, Mapo-gu, Seoul, Republic of Korea\n\n🔑 Your Suite Door Code\n \n\nCheck-in date in the format YYMMDD + *\n Example: 10 May 2025 → 250510* (remains the same throughout your stay)\n\n📶 Wi-Fi\n \n\nSSID: KT-GiGA_C34B\n \nPIN: eck93gg798\n\n🚗 Parking (Important)\n \n\nWe don’t have a private lot, but many guests park along the curb right beside the building.\n (Technically it isn’t legal, but enforcement is rare.)\n\n✅ Tip: If you plan to park on the curb (street-side), please message our team in advance — we’ll do our best to check the latest local parking situation for you.\n\n🅿️ Nearest official option (3-minute walk):\n\n Yeonnam-dong Public Parking Lot \n\n📍\n Map → https://naver.me/x0UvYEAj\n \n\nAddress: 361-9 Yeonnam-dong, Mapo-gu, Seoul\n \n\nRate: ₩300 per 5 minutes (no all-day pass)\n Discount: 50% off for multi-child families & eco-friendly vehicles\n\n📱 Guest Smartphone Provided\n\nA free smartphone with a Korean number and unlimited data & calls is available on the living room table.\n All essential apps are pre-installed, and it can be used as a portable Wi-Fi hotspot.\n\n💡 Local Tip: Open Naver Map → Bookmarks \n\n— we saved a local guide with\n hidden gem restaurants 🍜 supermarkets & convenience stores 🏪 hospitals & clinics 🏥 ATMs & banks 💳 and more 📍😉\n\n🍽️ Food Delivery Made Easy\n\nUse the guest smartphone to open Coupang Eats, create your cart, then send us a screenshot of your final order via Messenger.\n We’ll place the order using our card — you can pay us in cash (or crypto) at checkout.\n\n🚐 Need an MPV Van Taxi?\n\nLet us know anytime — we can help arrange a spacious ride using local peer-to-peer transport options.\n\n🍳 Kitchen Appliances\n\nA full kitchen is ready for you, including a dishwasher, oven, and water purifier.\n Feel free to cook like home! 🥘✨\n\n💧 Water Purifier (EVERPURE)\nBrand: EVERPURE (USA) — Starbucks official partner\n Type: Direct-flow purified water system\n Maintenance: Professionally serviced monthly\n How to use: Use the small faucet on the left side of the sink labeled “정수기 / Purified Water”\n Benefit: Safe, great-tasting water for drinking & cooking\n\n☕ Capsule Coffee & Tea\n\nExtra tea & coffee capsules are in the drawer under the induction range ☕✨\n\nilly Coffee Machine Guides\n \n\nQuick Start: https://youtu.be/XEDAXZY50FM?si=uOfwquZXC6WCis_G\n \n\nSteam Milk: https://youtu.be/bTzG7iM4dMA?si=aiEWUseiOT0as-Jo\n \n\nVolume Settings: https://youtu.be/h2X5gLYpf_4?si=eaDtARcyGQTjddFz\n\n♻️ Food Waste Disposal\n\nTurn on the sink water and press the foot pedal to use the disposer.\n\n🗑️ General & Recyclable Waste\n\nPlease separate trash into the bins in the kitchen.\n Extra trash bags are in the shoe cabinet — replace bags when full.\n\nWhen bags are full, leave them outside and message us.\n Korea’s trash rules can be tricky, so feel free to ask anytime 💛\n\n📽️ Multimedia Setup\n\nUse the projector connected to Korean TV & Google TV.\nSteps\nTurn on the projector\n\nTurn on the Yamaha soundbar\n\nUse the soundbar remote to choose input (TV or Google TV)\n\n\n🧴 Amenities & Towels\n\nAbout 20 towel sets (face/body/foot) are in the bathroom.\n Toilet paper: last compartment of the shoe cabinet\n Hotel-style amenities: cabinet beside the induction stove\n\n🔒 Privacy\n\nReflective window film protects your privacy during the day.\n At night, please close the blinds to stay fully private.\n\n❄️ Heating & Ventilation (Winter)\n\n🔥 Please don’t touch the living room heating panel (it controls the whole home + hot water).\n\n🌡️ Bedroom radiators: keep ON 24/7 and set to 23°C.\n\n🌬️ Ventilation (HRV) x2: keep ON (LOW setting) at all times to keep air fresh & prevent condensation.\n\n🧊 Feeling warm? Open a window for a few minutes.\n\n💬 Need help? Message us anytime!\n\n🚭 Smoking\n\nSmoking is allowed on the terrace only. Please use the ashtray 🙏","ts":1783495072463},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Our team will welcome you at home 😃","ts":1783495213629},{"sender":"Tom Hegdal","text":"Thank you very much Gaya. I will let them know. They are very excited","ts":1783495247699},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Safe travel @229691210346604 !","ts":1783495267847},{"sender":"Tom Hegdal","text":"I will see you tomorrow Gaya. My journey starts in 30 minutes. Thank you so much for all your help and patience with my large group.","ts":1783496779225}]},{"groupKey":"120363410279865987@g.us","name":"COZE SJ 13thAug Wesley Brown 4A2K","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"SJ","messageCount":16,"lastActive":1783495375059,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"@151432628060212  Hello :)","ts":1783469289608},{"sender":"Jacquette Brown","text":"Thank you","ts":1783484352161},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Home address by korean","ts":1783495319066},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"서울시 중구 칠패로 27 순화더샵아파트 B동 1207호","ts":1783495319669},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Main Gate Pin # 8 0 2 2","ts":1783495320258},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Main Door Pin 2 6 0 7 1 3 *","ts":1783495320857},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"[Naver Map]\nCOSE SJ_Our Town\nhttps://naver.me/xkqJwrTc","ts":1783495321449},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"The upper is the neighborhood map which includes qualified restaurants and attractions! (please sign up Naver and install Naver map !!!)","ts":1783495322049},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"*COZE SJ – STAY MANUAL*\n\n The Serviced Apartment Near Seoul Station Where Hotel Convenience Meets the Comfort of Home 🏡\n\n Welcome to your snug hideaway steps from Seoul Station!\n\n Kick off your shoes, relax, and let this warm-yet-witty guide show you how to keep our place peaceful, spotless, and altogether delightful.\n\n\n📌 Essential Information\n\nAddress — \n\n서울시 중구 칠패로 27 순화더샵아파트 B동 1207호\n\n #1207, APT B, Sunwha The Sharp APT\n27, Chilpae-ro, Jung-gu, Seoul, Republic of Korea 04511\n\nMain Gate Pin     # 8 0 2 2\n\nYour Suite Door Code — \n\nCheck‑in date in the format YYMMDD + *\n\nExample: 10 May 2025 → 250510* (remains the same throughout your stay)\n\nWi‑Fi Networks\n\nSSID  JOYHASLA_SJ\nPIN    joyjoyjoysj\n\n🏠 House Rules\n\n🏞️ A Peaceful, Respectful Neighborhood\n\nOur building prides itself on peace and quiet.\n\nAbsolutely no loud gatherings or shouting in the hallway—treat it like a museum corridor, not a karaoke lounge.\n\n\n🚪 Hallway Conduct\n\nThe hallway is a shared space. While we love a friendly “hello,” please keep voices low.\n\nDo not leave suitcases, boxes, or personal items in the hallway—even for a minute. It blocks the path and disturbs neighbors.\n\nBreaking these rules can lead to immediate penalties (nobody wants that).\n\n\n🚭 No Smoking Indoors\n\nThis is a strictly non-smoking home.\n\nLighting up indoors triggers a five-thousand-dollar fee for deep cleaning.\n\nSmoke detectors stand guard in every room (including bathrooms).\n\n\n🔇 Quiet Hours\n\nFrom around eight in the evening, keep noise to a minimum.\n\nIf neighbors complain about noise (music, rowdy chatter, door-slamming), your security deposit may disappear—no questions asked.\n\nWindows and doors should stay closed if you’re gaming, watching TV, or enjoying a private dance party.\n\n\n🪑 Furniture Placement\n\nKeep large furniture where it’s meant to be unless you’ve checked with us.\n\nSmaller items? Sure, move them if needed—just put them back before checkout.\n\n\n👶 Children\n\nLittles of all ages are very welcome.\n\nRemember to include them in your total guest count.\n\n\n👥 Registered Guests Only\n\nTo maintain safety and fairness, only registered guests may stay overnight.\n\nSurprise visitors or unregistered individuals can result in added fees or reservation cancellation.\n\nWe have an external camera at the entrance to ensure everyone’s security.\n\n\n🏡 Making Yourself at Home\n\n\n📱 Guest Smartphone Provided\n\nA smartphone with a Korean number and unlimited data & calls is provided free of charge during your stay!\n\nUse it to:\n\n🍽️ order food\n🚕 call taxis\n🌐 browse the web\n🗺️ navigate the neighborhood\n\nLocal Tip — Open the Naver Map app and check our bookmarks for:\n\n\n🍜 hidden‑gem restaurants\n \n🏪 convenience stores\n \n🏥 clinics\n\n💳 ATMs.\n\nIt’s like having a local guide in your pocket 📍😉\n\n🍽️ Food Delivery Made Easy\n\nOn the guest phone, open Coupang Eats.\nAdd items to your cart.\nScreenshot the cart and send it to us via WhatsApp.\nWe’ll place the order on our card; pay us later in cash or crypto at checkout.\n\n🚐 Need an MPV Van Taxi?\n\nSeats up to 7 passengers; fares ≈ 30 % higher than regular cabs.\nLet us know early if you need multiple vans or have heavy luggage.\n\n🍳 Kitchen & Appliances\n\nA full kitchen includes: dishwasher, oven, water purifier.\n\n💧 Water Purifier (EVERPURE)\nBrand: EVERPURE (USA) — Starbucks official partner\n\nType: Direct-flow purified water system\n\nMaintenance: Professionally serviced monthly\n\nHow to use: Use the small faucet on the left side of the sink labeled “정수기 / Purified Water.”\n\nBenefit: Very safe, great-tasting water for drinking & cooking\n\nFeel free to cook like home! \n\n☕ illy Coffee Machine\n\nCapsules are in the drawer under the coffee maker (or above the microwave). Enjoy anytime!\n\nNeed a quick tutorial? Check these links:\n\nQuick Start: https://youtu.be/XEDAXZY50FM?si=uOfwquZXC6WCis_G\n\nSteam Milk: https://youtu.be/bTzG7iM4dMA?si=aiEWUseiOT0as-Jo\n\nVolume Settings: https://youtu.be/h2X5gLYpf_4?si=eaDtARcyGQTjddFz\n\n\n\n♻️ Food Disposal\n\nTurn on water, press the pedal—watch scraps swirl away.\n\nNo bones or shells, please!\n\n\n📺 TV Streaming\n\nSwitch to Chromecast on the TV.\n\nStream Netflix, Disney Plus, or your favorite cat videos using the guest phone.\n\n\n🧻 Supplies & Towels\n\nTissues near the main door.\n\nTowels (face, body, foot) in the mirror closet, laundry nook, or dressing space.\n\n\n🎁 Amenities Box\n\nInside the staff closet in the dressing room, you’ll find extra goodies—use whatever you need.\n\n\n\n---\n\n😊 Thanks for Reading\n\nBy following these guidelines—especially around hallway conduct and quiet hours—you’ll help ensure a calm, pleasant stay for everyone. If you have questions, don’t hesitate to ask!\n\nEnjoy your time at COZE SJ Tailored Service Apartment near Seoul Station. We’re here to make your stay comfortable, relaxing, and hassle-free!","ts":1783495322652},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"🚐📚 The Complete Guidebook about Airport Vans!\n\n1️⃣ Reservation Method\n\nTell us your travel date , arrival time , airline , and flight number\nAfter confirmation, we’ll send detailed pickup instructions & driver contact.\n\n2️⃣ Van Service Rates & Promotions\n\n🎁 Promotions\n\n4-night stay → 1 × 7-seater van FREE \n6-night stay → 2 × 7-seater vans FREE \n\n💰 Extra Rates\n\nGimpo Airport ↔ Accommodation — 🚗 4-seater ₩70 000 / 🚐 7-seater ₩90 000\n\nIncheon Airport ↔ Accommodation — 🚗 4-seater ₩100 000 / 🚐 7-seater ₩120 000\n\nSeoul city luggage transport — 🚗/🚐 flat ₩60 000\n\n\n🛋️ Comfort Tip\n\nSeven people plus luggage can feel tight in a 7-seater. For more space, book two 4-seaters. 😌\n\n\n3️⃣ Meeting Your Driver\n\nYour driver tracks your flight and waits at the arrival gate with a name sign.\n\n⏳ Wait time up to 60 minutes after landing.\n\n🤝 Once you meet, head straight to the vehicle.\n\n💡 Tips required\n\nCurrency exchange or SIM?  The driver introduce you to find /  ₩10 000 \n\nEarly & Late Work Time (21PM-06AM) /  ₩20 000\n\n Baby Car Seat  / ₩20 000 per seat\n\nMove between termina /l ₩30 000 \n\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you soon! 🌷\n\nWarm regards,\nGaya, Guest Care Team \n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0\nAll you want, ALL-IN-ONE, All yours","ts":1783495371585},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Beyond travel agencies lies COZE — a band of hosts transforming Korean roads into your own curated adventure.\u000b\n\nCOZE Private Van Tour \u000b\u000b\n\n🚐 Vehicles & Base Rates (10 hours)  \u000b\n\n• Hyundai Staria (up to 10 guests) — ₩500,000  \u000b\n• • Hyundai County (up to 23 guests) — ₩800,000   \u000b\n• \u000bIncludes: ⛽ Fuel + 🅿 Parking + 🚧 Tolls   \u000b\n• \u000bNot included: 10 % VAT + 🍽 Meals + 🎟 Admission Fees\u000b\n\n👤 Tour Host | Speaking Korean English Japanese Chinese\n\n✨ Complimentary Comforts on Board \u000b\u000b\n\n📶 High-speed Wi-Fi \n🥤 Unlimited chilled bottled water \n🔌 USB-C / USB-A chargers \n♿ Loaner wheelchair (reserve ahead) \n👶 Free stroller rental & secure storage\n 🍼 Child & booster seats\n\n*Extra Charges\u000b*\n\n• Overtime — Staria ₩50,000/hr | County ₩100,000/hr \u000b\n\n• Distance Surcharge — +₩100,000 if total travel exceeds 150 km or extends beyond the Gyeonggi-area radius\n\n*Why COZE?\u000b*\n\n✅ Hosts who are passionate cultural interpreters, not just drivers \u000b\n✅ Fully personalized itineraries—hidden gems & authentic moments \u000b\n✅ Zero tourist traps or forced shopping stops \u000b\n✅ Honest, transparent pricing with no platform mark-ups\u000b\n\nPlus full concierge support for itinerary planning, restaurant bookings, special activities and more—everything tuned to your travel style.\u000b\n\nLet COZE take you beyond sightseeing and straight into the true heart of Korea!","ts":1783495372143},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Join COZE’s Cooking Class for a truly delicious Korean experience 🍳🇰🇷\nThis is not just a class — it’s a fun little food adventure! Visit a local market, discover fresh Korean ingredients, and learn how to make beloved Korean dishes with our friendly hosts. Expect good food, lots of laughs, and maybe a little flour on your clothes 😆🥬🍜\nCome hungry, leave happy, and take home tasty memories from Seoul 💛\n\nhttps://purple-variraptor-26e.notion.site/Seasonal-Korean-Cooking-Class-Slice-Mix-Sizzle-and-Share-Korean-Home-Cooking-Together-3678919e326f81a2b43cdc4a260b91c0?pvs=143","ts":1783495372724},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Step into your own K-drama moment in Seoul with our COZE Hanbok Photo Shoot 👘✨\n\nA professional photographer, stunning palace backdrops, and beautiful hanbok styling come together to create timeless photos for you, your partner, friends, or family.\nCheck details, sample images, and booking info here:\n\nhttps://hanbok-photo-shoot-famil-4ugms5e.gamma.site/","ts":1783495373312},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"Hi! 🎉 Celebrating something special during your stay? Let us do the decorating, so you can skip the balloon drama 😄\n\nCOZE Celebration is our in-room party styling service created with options like balloons, flowers, candles, cake, finger food, catering, and more.\nJust send us your preferred date and time, number of guests, concept or color theme, and whether you’d like finger food or catering, and we’ll take care of the rest 💛\n\nhttps://coze-celebration-hwjxrle.gamma.site/\n\nGaya, Guest Care Team of COZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783495373885},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"COZE isn’t just about a bed.\nWe’re here to share the true Seoul vibe and help you create unforgettable memories 🇰🇷💖\n\n Introducing COZE’s LOCAL EXPERIENCE CONTENTS! 🗺🤩\n\nhttps://purple-variraptor-26e.notion.site/COZE-PRIVATE-TOUR-2b58919e326f80209482f45bc01cd968?pvs=149","ts":1783495374466},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"*COZE eSIM 10% OFF 📱✨*\n\nLand in Korea, go online instantly!\n\nNo airport lines, no SIM-card hunting, no recharge stress.\nJust set up your eSIM before arrival and stay connected the moment you land 😊\n\nApply & pay easily through the Google Form below.\n\n🔗 https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdXQoDPivSiUw0Ryvk8nJFaUOAwJZdZak69BYErkJHkSSCz_A/viewform?pli=1⁠�\n\nGaya, Guest Care Team of COZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783495375059}]},{"groupKey":"wechat:26313916487@chatroom","name":"wechat:26313916487@chatroom","platform":"WeChat","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1783493662153,"messages":[{"sender":"wxid_i9piwpit0n7i12","text":"你好 住在你们这里真的很舒适很赞，现在已经回国啦～想问下你们用的洗发水是什么牌子？很好用，想自己买一瓶，方便的话可以告知一下麻，谢谢！","ts":1783474626873},{"sender":"wxid_i9piwpit0n7i12","text":"谢谢～","ts":1783474950194},{"sender":"wxid_d7u0w057nef622","text":"Thank you for the wonderful 5-star review!","ts":1783493662153}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:18294946740114616","name":"kakao:18294946740114616","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":6,"lastActive":1783492578284,"messages":[{"sender":"Unknown","text":"고수","ts":1783492367047},{"sender":"검은검과방패","text":"고수","ts":1783492367473},{"sender":"Unknown","text":"빼주세요","ts":1783492575957},{"sender":"Americium","text":"빼주세요","ts":1783492576127},{"sender":"Americium","text":"비누맛","ts":1783492578204},{"sender":"Unknown","text":"비누맛","ts":1783492578284}]},{"groupKey":"120363429055836995@g.us","name":"120363429055836995@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1783489618602,"messages":[{"sender":"Christoph Gebhard","text":"Hello everybody. We would like to take you up on your offer of a van to Incheon Airport. However, in addition to the one included in the price, we need a second van, as there are 9 of us plus our luggage. We would like to leave here at 6:00 a.m. on Friday so that we can arrive at the airport by 8:00 a.m.","ts":1783480640843},{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"sure! the extra charge costs 100K KRW for standard van extra 😀","ts":1783488956163},{"sender":"Christoph Gebhard","text":"That's fine for us 👍","ts":1783489618602}]},{"groupKey":"120363427591564695@g.us","name":"COZE JT 8thJul Yan Ertek 4A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"JT","messageCount":10,"lastActive":1783487877560,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @61847696863341 \n\nMy name is Cyrus Noh, and I’ll be your check-in host today.\n\nI’m here to help make your arrival smooth and comfortable, and to guide you through anything you may need for your check-in. 🏠✨\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783477394574},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"2:00 PM check-in is possible.\n\nCould you please let me know how you’ll be coming to the accommodation today, and where you’ll be departing from?\n\nWhen you leave your departure location, please send me a quick message with your estimated arrival time.\n\nI’ll be waiting near the accommodation entrance to welcome you and help with your check-in. 🏠✨","ts":1783477598514},{"sender":"Yan","text":"We will come around 1pm to seoul train station and take a taxi to home 👍🏼","ts":1783478006681},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Seoul Station pickup via I.M Taxi (van) 🚖\n\n👥 Capacity: up to 7 guests\n🧳 Luggage: up to 5 suitcases\n\nHow it works\n\n1. We don’t pre-assign a driver. Once you arrive at Seoul Station, please message us.\n\n\n2. If possible, let us know 3–4 minutes before you reach the pickup point.\n\n\n3. Our team will request an I.M Taxi van in real time and reply with the vehicle (plate) number and estimated pickup time.\n\n\n4. Meet the driver at the pickup point and confirm the plate number we send you.\n\n\n\nPlease keep your phone available for messages. If your timing changes, just give us a quick update—we’ll adjust right away. 💛\n\nCyrus, Guest Care Team of COZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783478139947},{"sender":"Егор","text":"Hello, we arrived in Seul and boarded the metro","ts":1783484237699},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Great, thank you for the update! 😊\nWhen you get off the subway at Hyehwa Station, please send me a message.","ts":1783484506897},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"I sent you the PDF file. 😊\nIt includes the directions to the accommodation, so please check it and follow the guide when you come.","ts":1783484644682},{"sender":"Егор","text":"We get off on huehwa station","ts":1783486061253},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"See you soon!","ts":1783486237463},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Check-in complete ✅\n\nIf you need anything, just message us here — the COZE team will help you. 😊","ts":1783487877560}]},{"groupKey":"120363409270801116@g.us","name":"COZE L9 7thJul Lai Cheung 4A1K","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"L9","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1783487810229,"messages":[{"sender":"Lai","text":"Thank you for the breakfast. Do you want to re use the box or can we make it small and put at the trash bin?","ts":1783487368559},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"🗑 Seoul Garbage Separation Guide\n(For foreign guests using this accommodation)\n\nWelcome to Seoul!🌆 Korea has a very strict garbage separation system. We will guide you through the following procedures so that you can easily follow them during your stay. Leave the rest to us ♻😊\n\n1️⃣ General garbage (일반 쓰레기 – incombustible)\n🧻 You can put it in:\n\nsmall plastic packaging, dirty wrapping paper\n\nused tissues, swabs, and sanitary products\n\nthe bones of a chicken-the bones of a large fish 🐔🐟\n\nRUBBER GLOVE, SPONGE, TOOTHBRUSH\n\n\n🚫 Do not take out garbage directly. Seoul's system is complicated.\n✅ Do this instead:\n\nUse a general trash can in the room\n\nseparate from recycled waste\n\n🛎 Please let the staff know when the trash can is full.\n\n\n2️⃣ Garbage (음 식물 레기) – food residue)\n🥕 You can put it in:\n\nRemaining rice, noodles, bread, fruits and vegetables\n\neggshells, coffee kasu ☕\n\na small fish bone\n\n\n🧯 Processing method:\n\nUse a kitchen disposer\n\nDrain 💧 Crush with soft residue\n⚠ No hard or fibrous substances (bone, shell, onion skin, corn skin, etc.) are allowed. The machine is going to break!\n\nthe bones and large residues of a chicken → To the general garbage\n\n\n3️⃣ Recycling (재활용) – Only those that are neatly separated)\n♻ Recycleable:\n\nPLASTICS 🧴: Bottle, takeout container (after washing)\n\nGlass 🍾: Wine bottle, bottle (no leftovers)\n\nPaper 📦: Newspapers, folded cardboard, clean paper boxes\n\nCan 🥫: Beverage can, food can (wash well)\n\nstyrofoam 🧊: Clean and dry stuff\n\n\n🗂 Processing method:\n🤢 dirty or leftovers → It's regular garbage!\n🛎 Please let the staff know when the trash can is full.\n\n4️⃣ Large garbage (대형 폐기물 – large garbage)\n🧳 For:\nSuitcases, furniture, mattresses, home appliances\n\n📞 Be sure to contact the accommodation manager before throwing it away.\n🚫 If you leave it in a public place, you will be fined.\n\n⚠ Precautions\n🚯 Illegal dumping = Fine 🧾\n🚫 Do not mix recycling, general garbage, or food waste\n♻ Use the correct trash can\n🙋♀ If you don't understand, please ask the staff!\n\n🌱 Thank you for your cooperation in keeping Seoul clean and green! Enjoy your stay. We will take care of the garbage 😄♻","ts":1783487705254},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"You can just place the box outside the door, near the trash bin. 😊\nNo need to fold it, as the box is a bit bulky. We will clear it every morning.","ts":1783487810229}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:443379230630620","name":"kakao:443379230630620","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":10,"lastActive":1783486553422,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE _ Jin","text":"성미산로23길 16-5 1층입니다","ts":1783486107016},{"sender":"COZE _ Jin","text":"성미산로23길 16-5 1층입니다","ts":1783486107134},{"sender":"팡팡수도설비","text":"네","ts":1783486127782},{"sender":"팡팡수도설비","text":"네","ts":1783486130008},{"sender":"COZE _ Jin","text":"동영상","ts":1783486172890},{"sender":"COZE _ Jin","text":"Video","ts":1783486172947},{"sender":"COZE _ Jin","text":"사장님 잠시보류요.다시 연락드릴게요","ts":1783486507860},{"sender":"COZE _ Jin","text":"사장님 잠시보류요.다시 연락드릴게요","ts":1783486508697},{"sender":"팡팡수도설비","text":"바로옆이라 출발했습니다","ts":1783486553004},{"sender":"팡팡수도설비","text":"바로옆이라 출발했습니다","ts":1783486553422}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:468897483159116","name":"kakao:468897483159116","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783482529968,"messages":[{"sender":"김소언","text":"{\"member\":{\"userId\":48718351,\"nickName\":\"김소언\"},\"kicked\":false,\"memorial\":false,\"hidden\":false,\"feedType\":2}","ts":1783482529968}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:473131976143563","name":"kakao:473131976143563","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":13,"lastActive":1783479473334,"messages":[{"sender":"한수지","text":"카드 결제 링크 보내주실 수 있나요?","ts":1783475402149},{"sender":"한수지","text":"카드 결제 링크 보내주실 수 있나요?","ts":1783475403439},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"네네!","ts":1783475844703},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"네네!","ts":1783475845427},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"저희가 감사의 마음을 담아 추가 인원에 대한 비용은 면제 처리 해드리겠습니다 ^^","ts":1783476067292},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"저희가 감사의 마음을 담아 추가 인원에 대한 비용은 면제 처리 해드리겠습니다 ^^","ts":1783476067822},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476080384},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476081922},{"sender":"서윤","text":"너무너무 감사합니다 좋은 하루 되세요~~~!","ts":1783476879802},{"sender":"서윤","text":"너무너무 감사합니다 좋은 하루 되세요~~~!","ts":1783476880149},{"sender":"한수지","text":"감사합니다!!!☺️","ts":1783476964248},{"sender":"한수지","text":"감사합니다!!!☺️","ts":1783476964268},{"sender":".","text":"{\"member\":{\"userId\":22403042,\"nickName\":\".\"},\"kicked\":false,\"memorial\":false,\"hidden\":true,\"feedType\":2}","ts":1783479473334}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:301321483004194","name":"kakao:301321483004194","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":8,"lastActive":1783478125613,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"기사님 배정 부탁드립니다","ts":1783477821150},{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"기사님 배정 부탁드립니다","ts":1783477821383},{"sender":"변이규","text":"변이규90","ts":1783477858096},{"sender":"변이규","text":"변이규90","ts":1783477858846},{"sender":"변이규","text":"젆형복110","ts":1783478117825},{"sender":"변이규","text":"젆형복110","ts":1783478118643},{"sender":"변이규","text":"전형복\n핸드폰 010 4766 7889","ts":1783478124223},{"sender":"변이규","text":"전형복\n핸드폰 010 4766 7889","ts":1783478125613}]},{"groupKey":"120363407384623871@g.us","name":"120363407384623871@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":2,"lastActive":1783477288199,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @188584162275518 \nYour check-in host today will be Ricky from our Guest Care Team.\n\nHe will help make your arrival smooth and comfortable, and guide you through anything you may need for your check-in. 🏠✨\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783477265811},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"when you go out to arrival hall, please find out your name board.","ts":1783477288199}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:473051438439374","name":"kakao:473051438439374","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":2,"lastActive":1783476181913,"messages":[{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면, 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476181075},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면, 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476181913}]},{"groupKey":"120363426846640888@g.us","name":"120363426846640888@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783475912325,"messages":[{"sender":"Ricky, Tour Host","text":"/exp jy 400000 tour","ts":1783475912325}]},{"groupKey":"wechat:26863426701@chatroom","name":"wechat:26863426701@chatroom","platform":"WeChat","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1783473440663,"messages":[{"sender":"wxid_1610706276821","text":"行李可以具体寄存哪里","ts":1783472576032},{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"2580*","ts":1783473237443},{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"Hello! Your luggage has been safely stored on the 1st floor.\n\nIf you arrive before 3:00 PM, you may enter the 1st floor with the password 2580 and take your luggage first.\n\n\nThank you! 🙏","ts":1783473440663}]},{"groupKey":"120363428539886519@g.us","name":"COZE JTS 8thJul Diana Li 1A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"JTS","messageCount":20,"lastActive":1783470726833,"messages":[{"sender":"D","text":"Hi there! My plane landed much earlier than","ts":1783455823955},{"sender":"D","text":"Just wanted to confirm if earlier check in is possible?","ts":1783455877864},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Yes! Your accommodation is fully ready for check-in, so you can check in now.\n\nPlease refer to the manual provided above. We wish you a safe journey to the property.","ts":1783457852776},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Yes! Your accommodation is fully ready for check-in, so you can check in now","ts":1783457886756},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Here we share the brief info of home and neighborhood!","ts":1783457947558},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Home address :","ts":1783457948115},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"서울특별시 종로구 낙산3길 27-1","ts":1783457948654},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Main Gate Key Box Pin 3 3 8 8","ts":1783457949214},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"(Please keep the key in the keybox. that key is shared)","ts":1783457990407},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Front Door Pin 260708 *","ts":1783458030604},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"House Manual","ts":1783458085578},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"The neighborhood information.\nyou can find all of info about our neighborhood  here!\nhttps://naver.me/5EaMQnFs","ts":1783458129178},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"🏠 COZE JTS Tailored Service Residence – Guest Manual\n\n👋 Welcome to COZE Hospitality 3.0!\nWe’re delighted to have you here in Daehakro(University Street)! To help you settle in comfortably, we’ve prepared this quick guide.\n\nHave a wonderful stay with COZE! 🏡✨\n\n📌 Essential Information\n\nAddress — \n\n서울특별시 종로구 낙산3길 27-1\n\n27-1, Naksan 3-gil, Jongno-gu, Seoul, Republic of Korea\n03088\n\nMain Gate Key Box Pin 3 3 8 8\n(please keep the key inside after use)\n\nYour Suite Door Code \n\n— Check‑in date in the format YYMMDD + *\n\nExample: 10 May 2025 → 250510* (remains the same throughout your stay)\n\nWi‑Fi Networks\n\nSSID  TEVA_STUDIO\nPIN  teva3388#*\n\n📱 Guest Smartphone Provided\n\nA smartphone with a Korean phone number and unlimited data & calls is provided free of charge during your stay!\nAll essential apps are pre-installed, and the phone can be used as a portable Wi-Fi hotspot.\n\nUse it to:\n🍽️ Order food\n🚕 Call taxis\n🌐 Browse the internet\n🗺️ Navigate the neighborhood\n\n💡 Local Tip:\nOpen the Naver Map app — we’ve bookmarked a detailed local guide with:\n🍜 Hidden gem restaurants\n🏪 Supermarkets & convenience stores\n🏥 Hospitals & clinics\n💳 ATMs & banks\n\nIt’s like having a local guide in your pocket 📍😉\n\n💡 Local Tip:\nCheck out the Naver Map app — we’ve bookmarked great local spots like restaurants, supermarkets, banks, clinics, and more. It’s like having a local guide in your pocket! 🗺📍\n\n🍽 Food Delivery Orders\nUse the guest smartphone to open the Coupang Eats app.\nAdd your items to the cart, take a screenshot of the final summary, and send it to us via Messenger.\nWe’ll place the order and pay for it. You can reimburse us in cash or cryptocurrency at checkout.\n\n🚖 MPV Taxi Booking\nWe can assist you with real-time bookings via IM TAXI.\nMPV taxis seat up to 7 people — ideal for groups. Fares are approx. 30% higher than standard taxis.\nNeed multiple vans? No problem — just expect a short delay.\n\n☕ Capsule Coffee & Tea\nExtra tea and coffee capsules are in the drawer beneath the living room tea cabinet. Feel free to help yourself!\n\nilly Coffee Machine\n\nQuick Guide\nhttps://youtu.be/XEDAXZY50FM?si=uOfwquZXC6WCis_G\n\nSteam Milk\nhttps://youtu.be/bTzG7iM4dMA?si=aiEWUseiOT0as-Jo\n\nProgram the Volume\nhttps://youtu.be/h2X5gLYpf_4?si=eaDtARcyGQTjddFz\n\n♻️ Food Waste Disposal\nA garbage disposal is built into the sink.\nTurn on the water, press the foot pedal, and it will grind away food waste.\n\n⚠️ No bones or shells, please!\n\n🗑️ Trash & Recycling\n\nInside of Main gate, You can find the big two trash bin. One is for general waste, The other is for \n\nIf it’s full, let us know — we’ll take care of it. Ask us about Korean waste rules anytime!\n\n🖥️ Office Desk Setup\nInstead of a TV, we’ve prepared a home office setup for your convenience. A 27-inch monitor and mini PC are connected to an all-in-one printer with unlimited ink — perfect for work or casual use.\n\n🧴 Supplies, Towels & Amenities\nExtra supplies, including tissues, body/face/foot towels, and a box of amenities are stored in the overhead cabinet above the bed. Please help yourself to anything you need!\n\n💬 Inquiries & Assistance\nNeed help or have any questions?\nJust message us anytime via Messenger!\nOur team will reply promptly to support you.\n\nWe're just one tap away — happy to help!\n\nEnjoy your stay with COZE and make yourself at home!","ts":1783458129740},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Yes, your room is all set, so you can check in now! \n\nPlease check the guide above, and hope you have a safe trip here.","ts":1783458174904},{"sender":"D","text":"Thank you so much :)","ts":1783459857633},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @86367581282366 \nMy name is Cyrus Noh, and I’ll be your check-in host for today.\n\nThe important self check-in details, including the password, are pinned at the top of this chat. Please check the pinned message when you arrive. 🏠✨\n\nAfter using the gate key, please return it to the key box right away. 🔑\n\nIf you have any questions or need anything, please feel free to let us know anytime.\n\nI’ll be around the accommodation area between 12:00 PM and 2:00 PM today, so if the timing works, I’d be happy to stop by briefly and say hello. 😊\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783470313958},{"sender":"D","text":"Hi Cyrus! Thank you so much, I have just arrived and already got in 👍🏻I would love to say hi but I have to leave for my appointment in a bit, hopefully I’d be able to say hello some other time 😊","ts":1783470459630},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Thank you so much for letting us know! 😊\nI’m glad to hear you arrived and checked in smoothly.\n\nNo worries at all — please enjoy your appointment.","ts":1783470544026},{"sender":"D","text":"Thank you for your hospitality 😊","ts":1783470567370},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Just a quick note about the shower 🚿\n\nThe shower head is installed on the ceiling, above the sink area.\nPlease use the faucet control near the sink, and switch the water direction using the small knob/lever on the faucet.\n\nOnce you switch it, the water will come down from the ceiling shower head. 😊\n\nIf you have any trouble, please let us know anytime.","ts":1783470726833}]},{"groupKey":"120363423605030782@g.us","name":"120363423605030782@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":2,"lastActive":1783467438166,"messages":[{"sender":"Anh","text":"Hi Gaya, just got the flight details. \nFlight number TG656\nJuly 13 06:55 terminal 1","ts":1783467268757},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Hello @127290012922015 \n\nWe have confirmed your flight information. We will arrange two vans for your arrival. \n\nWe look forward to seeing you on July 13th!","ts":1783467438166}]},{"groupKey":"120363427651504347@g.us","name":"COZE BS 20thDec Sophia Hwang 8A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"BS","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783451831340,"messages":[{"sender":"Sophia HWANG","text":"Thank you, Gaya.  Your information about future home plans gives me something to look forward to.  Even to people who canceled the reservation, you are showing the integrity of your service.  That is impressive.  Thank you & keep up the good work.  I'd like to keep your contact information or your email (if available) for future reference & I will recommend COZE to my friends for sure.","ts":1783451831340}]},{"groupKey":"120363411036797238@g.us","name":"COZE HT 15thSept Arianne Panganiban 8A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"HT","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1783435461976,"messages":[{"sender":"Arianne Panganiban","text":"Hi 😊","ts":1783434912320},{"sender":"Arianne Panganiban","text":"Thank you so much 😊","ts":1783435440307},{"sender":"Arianne Panganiban","text":"Cebu pacific  \nManila to seoul:\n sept 15 7:35pm - 12:45 am (incheon airport terminal 1)\n\nSeoul to manila\nSept 21 6:35 am - 9:55am (incheon ariport terminal 1)\n\nFlight details\n\nWill be total of 8 guest 😊","ts":1783435461976}]}]}